Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: gomobile.imageinfo
Version: 1.0dev-r3274
Summary: Unified interface to access image data in different Zope image objects
Home-page: http://www.twinapex.com
Author: Mikko Ohtamaa
Author-email: mikko.ohtamaa@twinapex.com
License: GPL
Description: Unified interface to access image data in different Zope image objects
        
        Return Python Imaging Library presentation of images:
        
        * Skin layer images, both file system based and ZMI uploads
        
        * Archetypes ATImage
        
        * Resource images (static media)
        
        Purpose
        -------
        
        This package is mainly used with Plone GoMobile project to dynamically reformat images to mobile presentation
        regardless how image was inputted to system.
        
        TODO
        ----
        
        * Management of external images: http:// image links, download and cache
        
